summary: Add a new arena type of dungeons where you gonna fight the gods of the norse, inspired by smite, who's basing it from real world myths. Recommended player level 30-50.
descriptionHtml:
[center][size=3][b][size=6]NORSE[/size][/b]
The Gods Battle Arena

Add a new arena type of dungeons level 10-100 where you gonna fight the gods of the norse,
inspired by smite, who's basing it from real world myths.
Recommended player level 30-50.

Note : Thor only outside during daytime.
[b]
[/b]Location :
Temple of Talos in Windhelm
[b]
[/b]Warning :
All the Gods have a 5000 basic health and
all the weapon are the daedric stats
[b]

Skyrim.bsa
Update.bsa
